# Vercel v2 (IMA camp) — always deploy summer camp after edits

After **any** change under `vercel-v2` that affects production (including from the `api/` workspace), run a **production deploy** to **`ima-summer-camp`**. Deploy from **project root** (parent of `api/`), not from `api/` alone:

```bash
cd /Users/tomrichardson/Downloads/vercel-v2 && VERCEL_ORG_ID=team_PXMrLfQ01zlse3XBsDcaPa3s VERCEL_PROJECT_ID=prj_TJxRFRbKAK4AkYBe8AKL1DoH2k9p npx vercel deploy --prod --yes
```

Do this at the end of the same turn as the edits unless the user says not to deploy.
